{
  "stem": "10710.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "On the first floor was the factory, where there was nothing there yet.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "All the machines were not mounted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were waiting for us to come.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we were supposed to be sleeping-- our quarters were supposed to be on top.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There were no beds.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We were sleeping on the straw for a few days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then they brought some bunks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But the bunks had only two floors.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "One on the bottom, one on the top.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And it was not enough.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So the youngsters my age were sleeping under the bunk.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You know, you put in there a little mattress there from straw and you couldn't move.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "You just slide in and that's how you slept for the night.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You couldn't move because if you moved, you picked up the other guy with the mattress.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So after a few weeks, they added another floor to the [NON-ENGLISH], to the bunks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And then we got the top thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It was already OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I was working in the beginning in the also in the road.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We used to-- we made the fences with those wires they shouldn't run.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We made those for the guards, those houses they should watch us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And then Mr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Banker that I knew from before who put me on the list, he saw that I'm working so hard.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And he said, I'll give you a better job.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "He gave me a job to work in a warehouse where we kept all the tools and all the supplies.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "It was like-- it was nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I was working there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I was somebody.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And the next door it was the warehouse from food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "So there was Dr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] He was running the food department.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And the warehouse was running-- [NON-ENGLISH], a German Jew.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
